==External links== *[http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/people-stewartry-given-flag-ahead-8147233#Ah5loRHu4g0EqIV0.97 People of the Stewartry given their own flag ahead of Queen's 90th birthday celebrations - Daily Record]
{{Subnational flags of the United Kingdom|Kirkcudbrightshire}}
